 The candidate of the All Progressive Congress (APC) for the Ibadan Southeast/Northeast Federal House of Representatives in Oyo state during the 2019 general election, Mr Deji Aboderin has defected to the ruling People’s Democratic Party. Aboderin served as the Senior Special Assistant on Public Affairs to former Governor Abiola Ajimobi. He cited many cases where party leadership worked against his electoral victory in the last election   Details later….